{"tid":83152,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不堪朋友嘲笑　英國男童彎刀自行割包皮","createTime":"2017-01-16T13:43:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-17T10:43:02.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"87fe37add4ae5431d8f40e8c172fda0a556c4867","tid":83152,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T13:43:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170115/photo/bknint-20170115171600946-0115_17011_001_01p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170115%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20170115171600946-0115_17011_001_01p.jpg&h=c268e905&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=N4UaHsWRcl1wj2iks0eoonvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=a2adc61c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】 不少專家都指出，孩童成長期間，朋輩的影響不容忽視。英國早前就有一名男童，懷疑因不堪朋友的嘲笑，而在家中以一把大彎刀為自己進行割包皮手術，導致下體大量出血，並自行到醫院求助。 <br />\n<br />\n據報道，受傷男童因為受到朋友的恫嚇，指他假若不進行割包皮手術，就永遠得不到女孩子的垂青。男童擔憂朋友的說話會成真，於是以彎刀割掉自己的包皮，導致下體大量出血。男童立即到醫院求醫，並花了兩天接受治療。 <br />\n<br />\n醫院內的一名醫生表示，不明白男孩的動機，因為當地社區有免費的上門割包皮手術；另有醫護人員為男孩的「勇敢」而感到震驚。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170115/bknint-20170115171600946-0115_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170115%2Fbknint-20170115171600946-0115_17011_001.html&d=N4UaHsWRcl1wj2iks0eoonvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=48f46894\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170115/bknint-20170115171600946-0115_17011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"dfb225b06b82635b849b07fd6eac7d89a62169a5","tid":83152,"uid":42097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T14:06:43.000Z","msg":"大刀砍龜頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06114f329d47c51e7a00aeef0e9397cc9b25190d","tid":83152,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T14:27:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\